<title>Eagle Publishing Job Opening</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/paper2.jpg">
<h2><center>Eagle Publishing Job Opening</H2></center>
<hr>
<h3><center>Print Buyer</h3></center>
Great print buying opportunity with rapidly growing politically conservative publisher.<p>
Experience in print industry required. Will work with department manager and assist marketers in meeting tight deadlines on book, newspaper, direct mail promotion, and newsletter publications.  Long hours, multiple projects, and professional fulfillment highly likely.<p>
Convenient Capitol Hill location. <p>

<center>
<i>Please send resume to:</i><br>
<b>Jim Zerr<br>
Production Manager<br>
Eagle Publishing, Inc.<br>
422 1st St., SE<br>
Washington, DC 20003<br></b>
<i>(no calls, please)</i><br>
