<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/lead-inst/eps.html 204.71.237.92 19970115092108 text/html 5080
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 15-Jan-97 09:21:33 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 04-Dec-96 16:22:44 GMT
Content-length: 4891
Content-type: text/html
