<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/townhall/columnists/chavez/chav061296.html 204.71.237.92 19970115093716 text/html 4747
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 15-Jan-97 09:37:41 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 14-Jun-96 17:45:12 GMT
