<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/townhall/columnists/devine/devi050796.html 204.71.237.92 19970115093947 text/html 7653
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 15-Jan-97 09:40:09 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 04-Jun-96 13:43:03 GMT
Content-length: 7466
Content-type: text/html
