http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/heritage/commentary/op-ef31.html 204.71.237.92 19970115095334 text/html 4842
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 15-Jan-97 09:53:59 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 03-Dec-96 14:10:15 GMT
