<DOCOLDNO>IA061-000339-B032-68</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/wash_times/fields.8-11.html 204.71.237.92 19970115100055 text/html 5572
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 15-Jan-97 10:01:12 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 05-Aug-96 13:50:34 GMT
