<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT27-B01-128</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA061-000341-B007-73</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/townhall/columnists/howley/howl030896.html 204.71.237.92 19970115101526 text/html 6811
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 15-Jan-97 10:15:39 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 22-May-96 15:54:22 GMT
