http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/townhall/columnists/rockwell/rock082296.html 204.71.237.92 19970115103314 text/html 8673
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 15-Jan-97 10:33:38 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 22-Aug-96 21:22:01 GMT
Content-length: 8485
