<P><LI> Apostolides A15.
<P><LI> U.S. Department of Justice, <I>Drug Legalization</I>.
<P><LI> "National Survey Finds Teen Drug Use Up,"<I> St. Louis Post-Dispatch</I> 13 December 1994: A-1.
<P><LI> Jonnes, 16 February 1995.
<P><LI> Jonnes.
<P><LI> Jonnes.
