<P><LI> Dennis Cauchon. "High Times Return,"<I> USA Today</I> 19 March 1993: D-2.
<P><LI> Cynthia Cotts, "Smart Money,"<I> Rolling Stone</I> 5 May 1994: 42-43.
<P><LI> Wayne J. Roques, personal interview, 20 February 1995.
