http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/heritage/kirk/kirklect.html 204.71.237.92 19970115114108 text/html 3495
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 15-Jan-97 11:41:31 GMT
